HOUSE BILL No. 1413
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 16-37-6.
Synopsis: Report on infant and maternal care. Requires the Indiana
department of health to prepare an annual report with specified
statistics that compare data from 2021 before abortion restrictions were
enacted with data from each subsequent calendar year.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Errington, Clere, Shackleford,
Bauer M
January 8, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Public Health.
2026 IN 1413—LS 6647/DI 104

